name: Quest Components
description:
These Quest Components for Figma is setup using auto-layout for responsiveness and designed using MUI based components such as buttons and checkboxes. With 100+ components, let this jump start your Product or Website.


By importing these components into Quest, you'll automatically convert them into working React components. Simply bring your custom Figma designs and design system and generate React components based on Material UI automatically. Easily export code that's as good or better than what a top-notch developer can write.


To learn more and request beta access, please visit:

https://quest.ai/react


The Quest Design System based on MUI is also coming soon.
